Package: MBVolDescrip
Title: Effect of Time or OTU Subsampling on Microbiome Volatility Estimates 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Anna", "Plantinga", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "amp9@williams.edu"), 
      person("Daniel", "Park", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Anna Plantinga <amp9@williams.edu>
Description: This package provides functions to subsample time points and/or read counts (rarefaction), as well as to compute ad hoc measures of volatility. Several publicly available microbiome time series datasets are included in the package for use exploring patterns of volatility with different subsampling choices.  
